Package org.liquidengine.legui.component

Class Dialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.liquidengine.legui.component.Component
      • org.liquidengine.legui.component.Widget
        • org.liquidengine.legui.component.Dialog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Dialog
extends Widget
    Dialog component is component which extended from Widget and have some additional functionality. On show(Frame) method it added to new created DialogLayer which forbid underlying layers to receive mouse click and keyboard events.
